These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-1::.
There 5 different types of food: cauliflower, garlic, lettuce, pumpkin, radish
There are 5 different nationalities: nigerian, turkish, indian, indonesian, french
1. the indonesian is in an odd position##4
2. the indonesian is in the middle##1
3. the person eating radish is on the left or right of the nigerian##3
4. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
5. the person eating cauliflower is between the indonesian and the indian##2
6. the person eating radish is in the middle##1
7. the indonesian is on the right of the french##1
8. the person eating pumpkin is on the left or right of the person eating radish##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |   3    |    4    |    5    |
| Food          | garlic | cauliflower | radish | pumpkin | lettuce |
| Nationality   | indian  | french      | indonesian   | nigerian     | turkish    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-2::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, fanta, iced-tea, tea, water
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: family, action, drama, sports, horror
1. the person drinking almond-milk is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
3. the person drinking water is in the middle##1
4. the person watching horror movies is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
5. the person watching family movies is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person watching sports movies##2
6. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |     2     |    3     |      4      |    5    |
| Beverage   | iced-tea     | tea       | water    | almond-milk | fanta   |
| Movie-Genre      | action | family | sports | horror      | drama |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-3::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: card-games, filmmaking, magic-tricks, reading, video-games
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: begonia, poppy, tulip, marigold, rose
1. the person who growsmarigold is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
2. the person who growspoppy is in an even position##4
3. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left or right of the person who growsbegonia##3
5. the person who growstulip is on the left or right of the person who growsbegonia##3
6. the person who growsrose is on the left or right of the person who growspoppy##3
7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
8. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3      |     4      |      5      |
| Hobby         | card-games | magic-tricks | filmmaking | reading    | video-games |
| Flower   | marigold     | begonia        | tulip      | poppy | rose      |

