.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-4::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: chess, puzzles, rock-climbing, sudoku, woodworking
There 5 different types of food: strawberry, blueberry, raspberry, peach, apple
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is in the middle##1
2. the person eating strawberry is in an even position##4
3. the person eating blueberry is on the far right##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person eating blueberry##1
5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person eating apple##1
6. the person who's hobby is puzzles is between the person eating raspberry and the person who's hobby is woodworking##2
7. the person eating apple is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |       3       |     4     |      5       |
| Hobby         | chess      | sudoku | rock-climbing | puzzles   | woodworking  |
| Food   | peach | apple    | raspberry        | strawberry | blueberry |

