.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-6::.
There 5 different types of food: cauliflower, mango, pineapple, spinach, pepper
The people have 5 different jobs:  electrician, engineer, paramedic, security-guard, software-developer
1. the person eating mango is on the far left##1
2. the engineer is between the software-developer and the person eating pineapple##2
3. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person eating cauliflower##1
4. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the engineer##1
5. the paramedic is the person eating pineapple##1
6. the paramedic is in an even position##4
7. the person eating spinach is on the left or right of the person eating cauliflower##3
8. the security-guard is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |         2          |    3     |     4     |       5        |
| Food   | mango        | cauliflower                | spinach  | pineapple  | pepper            |
| Job        | electrician | software-developer | engineer | paramedic | security-guard |

