.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: drama, crime, family, zombie, time-travel
The people have 5 different jobs:  doctor, electrician, firefighter, librarian, paramedic
1. the person watching zombie movies is on the left or right of the electrician##3
2. the paramedic is on the left or right of the electrician##3
3. the person watching crime movies is in the middle##1
4. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
5. the firefighter is in an odd position##4
6. the person watching drama movies is on the far right##1
7. the doctor is on the left or right of the person watching time-travel movies##3
8. the paramedic is on the right of the electrician##1
9. the librarian is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |      3      |     4     |       5       |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel       | family   | crime    | zombie    | drama |
| Job        | firefighter | doctor | electrician | paramedic | librarian     |

