.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-9::.
There are 5 different nationalities: chinese, egyptian, indian, indonesian, thai
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: january, july, february, december, november
1. the person who's birthday is in january is in an even position##4
2. the indonesian is the person who's birthday is in december##1
3. the person who's birthday is in december is the indonesian##1
4. the indonesian is on the far right##1
5. the egyptian is the person who's birthday is in january##1
6. the indian is between the egyptian and the chinese##2
7. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the indian##1
8. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Nationality   | thai | egyptian | indian     | chinese | indonesian |
| Birthday           | july | january     | february | november    | december      |

