2. the person playing go is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person playing scrabble is the accountant##1
4. the person playing bridge is on the right of the accountant##1
5. the person playing snooker is in an odd position##4
6. the lawyer is on the left of the dancer##1
7. the firefighter is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2    |      3      |     4      |    5    |
| Job     | lawyer | dancer | firefighter | accountant | analyst |
| Game   | go | domino | snooker    | scrabble    | bridge  |

