2. the person eating broccoli is on the left or right of the person watching fantasy movies##3
3. the person eating broccoli is between the person watching family movies and the person watching fantasy movies##2
4. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
5. the person watching horror movies is the person eating pepper##1
