.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-12::.
5 different pets are kept: fish, chinchilla, rabbit, turtle, cat
The people use 5 different means of transport: boat, bus, car, skateboard, trike
1. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the car##1
2. the person driving the trike is the owner of the fish##1
3. the person driving the trike is in the middle##1
4. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3
5. the person driving the bus is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person driving the boat is between the person driving the trike and the owner of the chinchilla##2
7. the person driving the bus is in an odd position##4
8. the person driving the bus is on the far left##1
9. the person driving the trike is on the right of the owner of the cat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2    |   3   |     4     |     5      |
| Pet        | turtle | cat | fish  | rabbit | chinchilla     |
| Transport   | bus  | car     | trike | boat      | skateboard |

