The people have 5 different jobs:  software-developer, dressmaker, paramedic, scientist, security-guard
1. the person drinking soy-milk is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
3. the scientist is on the far left##1
4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
5. the person drinking mirinda is in an even position##4
6. the person drinking iced-tea is between the software-developer and the person drinking mirinda##2
7. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the dressmaker##3
8. the software-developer is on the left of the paramedic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |     4      |    5     |
| Beverage      | tea       | mirinda | iced-tea | soy-milk   | coffee   |
| Job   | scientist | dressmaker | security-guard  | software-developer | paramedic |

