.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-14::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: thriller, martial-arts, superhero, mystery, time-travel
The people have 5 different hobbies: board-games, chess, dancing, traveling, woodworking
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
2. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
3. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
5. the person watching martial-arts movies is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left or right of the person watching superhero movies##3
7. the person who's hobby is traveling is between the person who's hobby is chess and the person watching martial-arts movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3      |     4     |     5      |
| Movie-Genre    | time-travel   | mystery  | martial-arts     | thriller | superhero |
| Hobby   | board-games | dancing | woodworking | traveling | chess      |

