.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-15::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: action, comedy, epic, martial-arts, mystery
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: october, july, december, april, june
1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3
2. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in april##3
3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
4. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
5. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3
6. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the person watching comedy movies##3
7. the person who's birthday is in december is in an odd position##4
8. the person who's birthday is in april is in the middle##1
9. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3       |    4     |    5    |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy  | epic    | martial-arts | action   | mystery |
| Birthday   | june | july | april    | october | december |

