.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-16::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  bartender, chef, designer, mechanic, police-officer
There 5 different types of food: kale, strawberry, pepper, cabbage, spinach
1. the mechanic is the person eating cabbage##1
2. the person eating pepper is in an even position##4
3. the chef is on the far right##1
4. the bartender is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating strawberry is on the far left##1
6. the bartender is on the left or right of the police-officer##3
7. the person eating kale is on the right of the police-officer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |    3     |    4     |   5    |
| Job           | bartender | police-officer | designer | mechanic | chef   |
| Food   | strawberry       | pepper            | kale    | cabbage     | spinach |

