.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-18::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: documentary, martial-arts, satire, scientific, zombie
The people have 5 different jobs:  police-officer, coach, social-worker, fisherman, scientist
1. the scientist is on the right of the police-officer##1
2. the coach is in an even position##4
3. the coach is on the right of the fisherman##1
4. the person watching zombie movies is on the left or right of the police-officer##3
5. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the fisherman##3
6. the scientist is on the far left or far right##3
7. the fisherman is on the left or right of the coach##3
8. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
9. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |     3      |   4    |     5      |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | martial-arts | zombie     | satire | scientific |
| Job     | fisherman       | coach   | social-worker | police-officer   | scientist        |

