.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-19::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: baking, card-games, cooking, photography, reading
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, montecristo, old-henry, oliveros, havana
1. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far left or far right##3
2. the old-henry-smoker is the old-henry-smoker##1
3. the oliveros-smoker is on the far left##1
4. the alhambra-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is reading##3
5. the person who's hobby is reading is between the person who's hobby is baking and the havana-smoker##2
6. the montecristo-smoker is between the person who's hobby is photography and the havana-smoker##2
7. the oliveros-smoker is in an odd position##4
8. the havana-smoker is the person who's hobby is card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Hobby         | photography | cooking | card-games | reading | baking     |
| Cigar   | oliveros    | montecristo   | havana       | old-henry | alhambra |

